                  </p>
               </sp>
               <sp who="a">
                  <p>S. I now <normalised orig="conceiv" auto="true">conceive</normalised> this <normalised orig="wel" auto="true">well</normalised><lb/>
enough. And <normalised orig="therfore" auto="true">therefore</normalised> I <normalised orig="intreat" auto="true">entreat</normalised><lb/>
