                  </p>
               </sp>
               <sp who="b">
                  <p>F. To that, I say, That if<lb/>
those Speculations have really<lb/>
no Influence at <normalised orig="al" auto="true">all</normalised> upon our<lb/>
Practice, then <normalised orig="ar" auto="true">are</normalised> they to be<lb/>
looked upon as <normalised orig="meer" auto="true">mere</normalised> Trifles, of<lb/>
