                     <lb/>
                     <fw type="pageNum" n="100">H2</fw>
                     <pb n="13"/>
                     <lb/>
according as that<lb/>
Influence is stronger or weaker.<lb/>
The fundamental Point of <normalised orig="al" auto="true">all</normalised><lb/>
Points, without which the<lb/>
