Influence of this is Universal,<lb/>
it being adapted to the natural<lb/>
<normalised orig="Facultys" auto="false">Faculties</normalised> of <normalised orig="al" auto="true">all</normalised> Mankind; and<lb/>
especially to work upon those<lb/>
