of God unto Salvation: and it<lb/>
is in effect the <notvariant>powerfullest</notvariant> Engine<lb/>
of <normalised orig="al" auto="true">all</normalised> others to <normalised orig="ingage" auto="true">engage</normalised><lb/>
Men to their <normalised orig="Dutys" auto="true">Duties</normalised>. There<lb/>
<normalised orig="ar" auto="true">are</normalised> other Points also, inferior<lb/>
indeed to this in Strength and<lb/>
general Usefulness, tho of a<lb/>
