on the other side received into<lb/>
<normalised orig="Mindes" auto="true">Minds</normalised> that <normalised orig="ar" auto="true">are</normalised> fitly disposed;<lb/>
Such Points or Articles (I<lb/>
mean) of Belief, as Work by<lb/>
a Principle of Love, and<lb/>
whose particular Foundation<lb/>
is in Christianity. But I <normalised orig="judg" auto="true">judge</normalised><lb/>
it not needful to branch out<lb/>
